message.body: I see you... Look up!
Heya- favor to ask. Any chance we could borrow tubes/rafts for monday? Have some but not enough. Wanting to take mom for a float down the brandywine...
Yea! For sure, I have tons. When ya wanna get 'em?
Heading out to downingtown now to visit victory. Later this eve maybe?
Shurrrrrmaybe. Gonna be in west phila, till I don't know when, but give a ring and we'll give it a go!
Ok, sounds good... I'm flexible. I'll give you a shout when we're back, we'll work something out. Thanks!! You are awesome!
No prob!

Heya! I'm back in town and my sorrows can only be drowned in beer and river water...any chance I can nab those tubes from ya sometime soonish? And do you want to go (birthday toob on the 17th and possibly before!)
Hey! You around your place? Just got home, but heading out again in a bit. Can do toob drop if you're available...
Sorry! Will be around tomorrow?
Hey- I'm suddenly only a maybe for tomorrow- are you around today our tonight to receive toobz just in case?
Not tomorrow, Sunday! Jeremy is around today to receive toobz tho...but hope you can come! Lemme know so I have a count for the car!
Sunday! Don't know how I got that mixed up. Ok, that may work better...
Ok! When can you let me know?
Ok... In for tomorrow! If you still have space for me... Don't think I can wrangle a car
Should be good! See ya in the morn round 9!
Hey! would it be be possible to swing by and grab me from/near my house in a car? Not sure I should attempt biking all those tubes. Can walk but it'll be a bit
Shurrre. It's just you right? I'll letcha know when we head over. Also, hadta get a carshare, $10 a person
Sounds good... Thanks!
Heya! Got a request to see if you and yr cornhole game would like to come to an awesome hoedown tonight! Ride provided for ya both!
Oh, rats! I'm already planned up for the evening and my cornhole boards are loaned out! Have fun though!
Thanks anyway! And we need to hang soon!
Post thanksgiving feast! Friday at a location soon to be decided...celebrate year 2 of our tradition of eating a seitan loaf shaped like the object/animal of our choice.
Heya! Our show in Knoxville is tonight at the birdhouse. If you know anyone who might like it, send em our way! Thx!!
Sent messages to the puppet-lovers and art heads in K-town... Hope you get a good crowd! How's it been so far? Break a leg tonight!
Thx so much! It's been great so far!
